## OverlaidForm pre-fill extension recap

Added small, broadly useful extension to `injectRowData` in `OverlaidForm.tsx`:

- Optional per-field `sourcePath: string` — read pre-fill from a dotted path on rowData instead of `rowData[field.name]`.
- Optional per-field `sourceParseJson: boolean` — JSON.parse the value at sourcePath before drilling further.
- Optional per-field `sourceSubPath: string` — second dotted-path drill after parse.

Default behavior unchanged (`rowData[field.name]`) so all existing forms keep working. Mirrors the KeyValueGrid `parseJson`/`subPath` pattern; future forms that need to read from stringified JSON entity fields use this without bespoke plumbing.

